abstract: >-
  TerminalPad is the home screen for your terminal on macOS — an AI agent and
  CLI launcher that opens any AI coding agent (Claude Code, Gemini CLI, Ollama,
  OpenCode, Cursor and more) or installed command-line tool in one keystroke.
